Ranger Help for: repair
=======================

SYNTAX:      repair quiver
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Refreshes your existing quiver, fixing any issues with it. This
destroys your current quiver and creates a fresh one, restoring
your command paths and guild functionality.

If you have completely lost your quiver, use 'rebuild quiver'
instead.

=============================================================================
